OL,7,FA covert surveillance operation
OL,8,Fauthorised by a Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fpolice chief in a bid to unmask a
OL,10,Fjournalistic source was unlawful, a
OL,11,Ftribunal has ruled.
OL,13,FThe Investigatory Powers Tribunal
OL,14,Fquashed the decision made by former
OL,15,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fchief constable Sir George Hamilton,
OL,17,Fto approve the Directed Surveillance
OL,18,FAuthorisation (DSA) in an
OL,19,Finvestigation into the leaking of a
OL,20,Fconfidential document that appeared in
OL,21,Fa documentary on a Troubles massacre.
