OL,7,FThe tribunal, chaired by Lord Justice
OL,8,FSingh, also awarded damages of #4,000
OL,9,Feach to documentary makers Barry
OL,10,FMcCaffrey and Trevor Birney, in a
OL,11,Fjudgment issued on Tuesday.
OL,13,FThe IPT had been examining allegations
OL,14,Fthat the award-winning journalists
OL,15,Fwere subject to unlawful covert
OL,16,Fsurveillance by UK authorities.
