OL,7,FThe tribunal also looked at separate
OL,8,Fallegations that the PSNI and the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police in London
OL,10,Funlawfully accessed Mr McCaffrey's
OL,11,Fphone data in unrelated operations, in
OL,12,F2013 and 2012 respectively.
OL,14,FThe two forces had already conceded
OL,15,Fthat those 2012 and 2013 operations
OL,16,Fwere unlawful.
OL,18,FThe tribunal also quashed the two
OL,19,Fauthorisations for those two phone
OL,20,Fdata operations, but did not award any
OL,21,Fdamages to Mr McCaffrey in those cases.
