OL,7,FIn 2018, Belfast-based Mr McCaffrey
OL,8,Fand Mr Birney were controversially
OL,9,Farrested as part of a police
OL,10,Finvestigation into the alleged leaking
OL,11,Fof a confidential document that
OL,12,Fappeared in a documentary they made on
OL,13,Fthe 1994 loyalist paramilitary
OL,14,Fmassacre in Loughinisland, Co Down.
