OL,7,FThe Police Service of Northern
OL,8,FIreland, citing a conflict of
OL,9,Finterest, asked Durham Police to lead
OL,10,Fthe investigation into the inclusion
OL,11,Fof the Police Ombudsman for Northern
OL,12,FIreland document in the No Stone
OL,13,FUnturned film on the UVF pub shooting
OL,14,Fthat claimed the lives of six men.
OL,16,FThe PSNI later unreservedly apologised
OL,17,Ffor the way the men had been treated
OL,18,Fand agreed to pay #875,000 in damages
OL,19,Fto the journalists and the film
OL,20,Fcompany behind the documentary.
