OL,7,FIn court proceedings earlier this
OL,8,Fyear, the tribunal heard that a
OL,9,Fdetective requested the DSA from Sir
OL,10,FGeorge in order to monitor whether the
OL,11,Ftwo reporters would reach out to their
OL,12,Fsource in the week after their initial
OL,13,Frelease from custody.
OL,15,FSir George gave the green light for
OL,16,Fthe covert surveillance of an
OL,17,Findividual whom officers suspected of
OL,18,Fbeing the source of the leaked
OL,19,Fdocument from the Police Ombudsman's
OL,20,Foffice.
