OL,7,FIn its judgment, the IPT said: "We
OL,8,Fwill quash the DSA. We have determined
OL,9,Fthat a declaration of its unlawfulness
OL,10,Fwould not be sufficient to afford the
OL,11,Fclaimants just satisfaction in respect
OL,12,Fof its incompatibility with the rights
OL,13,Fprotected by Article 10 (of the
OL,14,FEuropean Convention of Human Rights)."
OL,16,FReacting to the judgment, Mr Birney
OL,17,Fand Mr McCaffrey both called for a
OL,18,Fpublic inquiry into police
OL,19,Fsurveillance of journalists.
