OL,7,F"I accept the Investigatory Powers
OL,8,FTribunal's judgment that due
OL,9,Fconsideration was not given to whether
OL,10,Fthere was an overriding public
OL,11,Finterest in interfering with
OL,12,Fjournalistic sources before
OL,13,Fauthorising surveillance, which
OL,14,Fimportantly, although it was not
OL,15,Fdirected toward the journalists Mr
OL,16,FMcCaffrey and Mr Birney, it did impact
OL,17,Fthem in 2018," he said.
