OL,7,F"This was one of a number of difficult
OL,8,Fdecisions on a complex and fast-moving
OL,9,Fday for policing in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Finvolving balancing competing
OL,11,Finterests at pace.
OL,13,F"Separately the Tribunal found that
OL,14,Falthough officers complied with UK law
OL,15,Fand procedure at the time, a 2013
OL,16,Fauthorisation for communications data
OL,17,Fwas a breach of our human rights
OL,18,Fobligations. I am pleased that the
OL,19,FTribunal found officers acted in good
OL,20,Ffaith.
